wiki.content:
Through the Wire is the lead single from  Kanye West's  debut album The College Dropout (2004). It samples Chaka Khan's 1985 single "Through the Fire".
        
User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License and may also be available under the GNU FDL.
wiki.summary: Through the Wire is the lead single from  Kanye West's  debut album The College Dropout (2004). It samples Chaka Khan's 1985 single "Through the Fire".
